ellow (?).Of preparing the panel.628.TO PREPARE A PANEL FOR PAINTING ON.The panel should be cypress or pear or service-t
ree or walnut. Youmust coat it over with mastic and turpentine twice distilled andwhite or, if you like, lime, and put i
