PURPLE.Powder gall nuts and let this stand 8 days in the white wine; and inthe same way dissolve vitriol in water, and l
et the water stand andsettle very clear, and the wine likewise, each by itself, and strainthem well; and when you dilute
 the white wine with the water thewine will become red.647.Put marcasite into aqua fortis and if it turns green, know th
