t the time.On history of astronomy.915.Cicero says in [his book] De Divinatione that Astrology has beenpractised five hu
ndred seventy thousand years before the Trojan war.57000.[Footnote: The statement that CICERO, _De Divin._ ascribes thed
iscovery of astrology to a period 57000 years before the Trojan warI believe to be quite erroneous. According to ERNESTI
, _ClavisCiceroniana,_ CH. G. SCHULZ (_Lexic. Cicer._) and the edition of _DeDivin._ by GIESE the word Astrologia occurs
