Magnificent President, I...Magnificent President:--Having ofttimes remembered the proposalsmade many times to me by your
 Excellency, I take the liberty ofwriting to remind your Lordship of the promise made to me at my lastdeparture, that is
 the possession of the twelve inches of watergranted to me by the most Christian King. Your Lordship knows that Idid not
