heet containing the studyfor the said cartoon, has evidently no reference to the drawing onwhich it is written but is ob
viously of the same date. Though I havenot any opening here for discussing this question of the cartoon, itseemed to me
important to point out that the character of thewriting in this note does not confirm the opinion hitherto held thatthe
Royal Academy cartoon was the one described by Vasari, but, onthe contrary, supports the hypothesis put forward by Mr. M
